high_descs: Turn right and then right again to the white table on the left wall.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Put the fork in the  yellow cup.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink to the right of the drain.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork in it in a sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go to window, turn right, go to table.
Pick up the fork to the left on the table.
Put the fork in the orange cup on the table.
Pick up the cup with fork on the table.
Turn right, bring the cup to the sink, turn right to face the sink.
Put the cup with fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the window, then turn right again and go to the table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Put the fork in the cup.
Pick up the cup with the fork.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the cup and fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a cup in the sink.
